- Description of the incident
- Relevant timestamps or evidence
- Any supporting context

All reports will be reviewed confidentially.

---

## 7. Enforcement

Violations of this Code of Conduct may result in:

- Warning or formal notice
- Temporary suspension of access
- Permanent removal from the project
- Legal action in severe cases involving intellectual property theft or malicious activity

All enforcement decisions are made at the discretion of Vexel Innovations leadership.

---

## 8. Scope

This Code of Conduct applies to:

- All repositories owned by Vexel Innovations
- Internal communication channels
- Issue trackers, pull requests, and discussions
- Any interaction representing the organization publicly or privately

---

## 9. Acknowledgment

By accessing or contributing to this project, you agree to comply with this Code of Conduct.

Failure to comply may result in loss of access and other actions deemed necessary.
